OpenAI’s GPT-5 is the next-generation language model set to succeed GPT-4, and it’s already in training. As of July 2025, OpenAI has confirmed that GPT-5 is expected to release before the end of the year. It will bring improved reasoning, memory, reliability, and possibly multimodal capabilities that are better than anything seen so far. This article breaks down everything you need to know: what GPT-5 is, what it can do, how it compares to current models, and what it means for users and developers. https://www.blockchain-council.org/certifications/certified-bitcoin-expert-cbie/
